@startuml
title Szenario 5: Zusammenbau der Puzzleteile

hide footbox

participant "Input" as IN
participant "Preparation" as PREP
participant "Anchor\nSelection" as ANCHOR
participant "Piece\nPlacement" as PLACE
participant "Visualization" as VIS
participant "Output" as OUT

IN -> PREP: edge_solver_results\n(chains, connections)

PREP -> PREP: 1. Calculate\ncentroids & chains

PREP -> PREP: 2. Normalize orientations\n(blue dots → upward)

PREP -> ANCHOR: Prepared pieces

ANCHOR -> ANCHOR: 3. Select anchor piece\n(highest connection score)

ANCHOR -> PLACE: 4. Place anchor at origin\nT₀ = {pos:(0,0), rot:calc}

loop for piece 1 to N-1
    PLACE -> PLACE: 5. Find best connection\nto placed pieces

    PLACE -> PLACE: 6. Translate:\nblue_dot → anchor_blue_dot

    PLACE -> PLACE: 7. Rotate around blue_dot:\nalign red_dot with anchor_red_dot

    PLACE -> PLACE: Store: Tᵢ = {pos, rot}
end

PLACE -> VIS: All pieces placed

VIS -> VIS: 8. Generate 8 steps:\n- Centroids\n- Orientations\n- Anchor selection\n- Placements (1-4)\n- Complete assembly

VIS -> OUT: assembly_steps_combined.png

@enduml
